 BLACKPINK 的 Lisa 成立了自己的经纪公司 LLOUD https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-lisa-launch-own-artist-management-company-lloud-3584291?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=blackpink-lisa-launch-own-artist-management-公司大声Puah ZiweiThu, 08 Feb 2024 08:10:56 +0000 Music NewsNewsK-pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3584291 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/blackpink-lisa-lloud-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Blackpink 丽莎·卢德" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/blackpink-lisa-lloud-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/blackpink-lisa-lloud-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/blackpink-lisa-lloud-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/blackpink-lisa-lloud-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/blackpink-lisa-lloud-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/blackpink-lisa-lloud-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>泰国韩国流行偶像将其描述为“展示我在音乐和娱乐方面的愿景的平台”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-lisa-launch-own-artist-management-company-lloud-3584291">BLACKPINK 的 Lisa 成立自己的经纪公司后，LLOUD</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/blackpink-lisa-lloud-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Blackpink 丽莎·卢德" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/blackpink-lisa-lloud-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/blackpink-lisa-lloud-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/blackpink-lisa-lloud-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/blackpink-lisa-lloud-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content